69-1876. Editors: Luman Foote, 1827-<1832>; D.W.C. Clarke, <1850>-1853; G.W. Benedict, 1853-<1863>; G.G. Benedict, 1854-<1863>. Issues for <July 6, 1827-> called: <volume 1, number 4-> Daily eds.: Daily free press (Burlington, Vt.), Apr. 1, 1848-July 9, 1868, and: Burlington daily free press (Burlington, Vt. : 1868), July 10-Dec. 31, 1868. Other weekly eds.: Times (Burlington, Vt. : 1858), 1858-1861, and: Burlington times (Burlington, Vt. : 1861), 1861-1865. Vol. IX, No. 45 (January 8, 1836); title from caption (Chronicling America's website, viewed Feb. 2, 2021). Vol. XXXIV, Number 27 = New Series Vol. XII (Dec. 29, 1865) (Chronicling America's website, viewed Feb. 2, 2021). Burlington weekly free press"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:17.248Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2021220095/", "image_url": [], "index": 12, "language": ["english"], "location": ["chittenden", "vermont", "burlington", "united states"], "number": ["online resource", "2021220095", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "778030029", "2767-259x"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Weekly free press"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "burlington free press (burlington, vt.) 1827-1865 [online resource]"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 49.72571, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["newspapers", "united states", "burlington (vt.)", "burlington", "chittenden", "vermont"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:01:49.831Z", "title": "Burlington free press", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2021220095/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn84023127/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn84023127"], "batch": ["vtu_adamant_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "contributor": ["benedict, g. g. (george grenville)", "foote, luman", "benedict, george wyllys", "cl